==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Heredity
<hw>He*red"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>hereditas</ets> heirship.]</ety> <fld>(Biol.)</fld> <def>Hereditary
transmission of the physical and psychical qualities of parents to their
offspring; the biological law by which living beings tend to repeat
their characteristics in their descendants. See
<er>Pangenesis</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hereford</ent>⟦br⟧
